'''Kyle Rowling''' is a fight director who worked on both [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Rowling doubled for [[Christopher Lee]], General Grievous and [[Samuel L. Jackson]].<ref name=":0">''[[It's All For Real: The Stunts of Episode III]]''</ref>

